{"tid":1928412,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"5個打1個都打唔撚贏，渣既","createTime":"2020-03-16T11:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T11:52:52.000Z","uid":213877,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9691e8aa7b5b3b3b28193a826b5ac2007f4fa927","tid":1928412,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"旺角鬧市紅褲怒漢1揪5 磚頭掟敗走私家車<br />\n<br />\n今早8時許，有網民於facebook上傳2片段，指旺角發生「1揪5」事件。1名身材高大的紅褲漢，與5名年輕男子在花園街上演全武行，他追打當中一名金毛男，數度拍打其頭部，同伴護救一度憤而起腳還擊，卻不敵連環拳，一番混戰後，5人黨不敵登車離開，卻在亞皆老街鬧市中，被紅褲漢追趕以磚頭掟車。<br />\n《香港01》向警方查詢事件，警方稱今天旺角區未有收到類似案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/448448/旺角鬧市紅褲怒漢1揪5-磚頭掟敗走私家車\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F448448%2F%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%AC%A7%E5%B8%82%E7%B4%85%E8%A4%B2%E6%80%92%E6%BC%A21%E6%8F%AA5-%E7%A3%9A%E9%A0%AD%E6%8E%9F%E6%95%97%E8%B5%B0%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=97b6eea9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/448448/旺角鬧市紅褲怒漢1揪5-磚頭掟敗走私家車</a>"},{"pid":"96b58487c0c9d5e41b1f405968a7f13817f9090e","tid":1928412,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4163719/org/261a03510878e0a7af489b06812029fb.jpg/AgdTusuNKeALs30qEg_88oXyFpVjson0CTmxhQk5sYU?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4163719%2Forg%2F261a03510878e0a7af489b06812029fb.jpg%2FAgdTusuNKeALs30qEg_88oXyFpVjson0CTmxhQk5sYU%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=b6ab35d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1528288304f1a752c85ee25fed5a47276b6fee6","tid":1928412,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c0a917b5c8093ea69bf4271133f6b58e03ed2d2","tid":1928412,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted